                    "spell_name": "Improved Invisibility",
                    "range": "touch",
                    "duration": "4 rounds + 1 round per CA level",
                    "reversible": false,
                    "pp": 207,
                    "spell_desc": "<p>Functions as the <i>invisibility</i> spell (q.v.), except that its recipient (human, humanoid, or giant) can attack or cast harmful spells at enemies without reappearing in exchange for a more limited spell duration. The invisible person\u2019s attacks, however, cause a slight shimmer or vibration in the air around them, allowing enemies to distinguish their approximate whereabouts; hence enemies can counterattack, though the invisible person enjoys a +4 AC bonus.</p>"
